{"sections":{"main":{"type":"article-template","custom_css":[".article .section-header__title {text-transform: none;}","header.section-header {margin: 0;}"],"settings":{"image_hero":false,"blog_show_tags":true,"blog_show_date":false,"blog_show_comments":false,"blog_show_author":false,"social_sharing_blog":false}},"background_image_text_GXGKcF":{"type":"background-image-text","custom_css":[],"settings":{"classes":"custom-banner-img","subtitle":"","title":"","text":"","text_color":"#000000","button_label":"","button_link":"","bg_color":"#000000","btn_color":"#ffffff","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/rsz_mdm_ago20_ec_0768__1.jpg","layout":"left","height":550,"framed":false,"parallax":false,"parallax_direction":"top","lazyload_images":true}},"rich_text_X4YKkz":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"text_reYjpA":{"type":"text","settings":{"enlarge_text":false,"text":"<p>Selecting the right men’s ring can elevate your look for any occasion, whether it's for a formal event, a wedding, or everyday wear.<\/p><p><\/p><p>MARCO DAL MASO offers a refined selection that blends timeless craftsmanship with modern aesthetics. Here’s a guide to help you choose the perfect ring based on the occasion and the best materials from our exclusive men's jewelry collection.<\/p>"}},"text_iNFK7m":{"type":"text","settings":{"enlarge_text":false,"text":"<p><strong>Formal Events<\/strong><\/p><p><\/p><p>For formal occasions, choosing a ring that complements your outfit and adds a touch of elegance is essential. Rings from MARCO DAL MASO for formal events are designed to be sleek and sophisticated, making a statement without overpowering your outfit.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["text_reYjpA","text_iNFK7m"],"settings":{"desktop_hide":false,"mobile_hide":false,"align_text":"left","narrow_column":false,"divider":false,"padding_b":0}},"text_columns_Nfdzmj":{"type":"text-columns","blocks":{"text_block_WDbC73":{"type":"text_block","settings":{"enable_image":true,"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/AGAN59-06BLSBER_01a02969-ee9c-4b67-bfca-ed3e109de6ad.jpg","image_mask":"square","image_width":650,"title":"","text":"<p><strong>Vermeil Rings: <\/strong>Vermeil, a gold-plated silver, offers the luxurious appearance of gold without the hefty price tag. Its bright, polished finish adds a classy, timeless feel to formal looks. <\/p><p>Opt for vermeil rings if you want to make a subtle, but luxurious statement.<\/p>","style_link":false,"chat_btn":false,"button_label":"","button_link":""}},"text_block_yPAbAB":{"type":"text_block","settings":{"enable_image":true,"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/rsz_agan0060-01pi-e2.jpg","image_mask":"square","image_width":650,"title":"","text":"<p><strong>Oxidized Silver Rings<\/strong>: If your style leans more toward modern and edgy, oxidized silver is a great choice. Its dark, matte finish contrasts well with black-tie attire, adding depth and character to your overall look. <\/p><p><\/p><p>These rings stand out without overshadowing your formal wear, giving off a subtle, rugged elegance.<\/p>","style_link":false,"chat_btn":false,"button_label":"","button_link":""}}},"block_order":["text_block_WDbC73","text_block_yPAbAB"],"custom_css":["@media screen and (max-width: 767px) {.grid--flush-bottom > .grid__item:first-child {display: flex; flex-direction: column-reverse; }}"],"settings":{"title":"","btntext":"","btnurl":"","text":"","align_text":"left","divider":false,"mobile_link":""}},"rich_text_cAqpJe":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"text_xM6FrM":{"type":"text","settings":{"enlarge_text":false,"text":"<p><strong>Wedding Rings<\/strong><\/p><p><\/p><p>Your wedding ring should be both stylish and symbolic, reflecting your personality and commitment. MARCO DAL MASO’s Continuum collection includes designs that are timeless and contemporary, using materials crafted to stand the test of time.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["text_xM6FrM"],"settings":{"desktop_hide":false,"mobile_hide":false,"align_text":"left","narrow_column":false,"divider":false,"padding_b":0}},"text_columns_LhgQnR":{"type":"text-columns","blocks":{"text_block_ptGBqY":{"type":"text_block","settings":{"enable_image":false,"image_mask":"none","image_width":650,"title":"","text":"<p><strong>Black Diamond Rings: <\/strong>For men looking to break tradition, black diamond rings offer a bold, unique style. Their sleek, masculine feel, makes them a popular choice in modern men’s wedding rings.<\/p>","style_link":false,"chat_btn":false,"button_label":"","button_link":""}},"text_block_QrmpDV":{"type":"text_block","settings":{"enable_image":false,"image_mask":"none","image_width":650,"title":"","text":"<p><strong>Classic Gold Bands: <\/strong>There’s a reason classic gold bands never go out of style. This timeless option is elegant and refined, embodying both tradition and modern appeal. It's an excellent choice for men who value classic design with a hint of luxury.<\/p>","style_link":false,"chat_btn":false,"button_label":"","button_link":""}}},"block_order":["text_block_ptGBqY","text_block_QrmpDV"],"custom_css":["@media screen and (max-width: 767px) {.tci .grid--flush-bottom > .grid__item:last-child {margin-bottom: 0; } .tci {padding-bottom: 0; }}"],"settings":{"title":"","btntext":"","btnurl":"","text":"","align_text":"left","divider":false,"mobile_link":""}},"text_columns_MdreXB":{"type":"text-columns","blocks":{"text_block_FQkTEP":{"type":"text_block","settings":{"enable_image":true,"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/GIAN0911-01YE_7_76f52be3-4acd-4f7c-a604-bb683f8a2057.jpg","image_mask":"square","image_width":650,"title":"","text":"","style_link":false,"chat_btn":false,"button_label":"","button_link":"shopify:\/\/products\/moneta-pave-signet-ring-oxidized-silver-with-black-diamonds-and-tsavorite-agan0055-06bv"}},"text_block_TrdrQP":{"type":"text_block","settings":{"enable_image":true,"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/AMBIENTATO_ANELLI_ORO_555f5277-b20f-44e3-9b21-d3d617d70ddb.jpg","image_mask":"square","image_width":650,"title":"","text":"","style_link":false,"chat_b